    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hideko is a short mystery game about nature. ☀️☁️🍃</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the rules of a small sandbox world to create new objects, plants and other forms of life! Discover special situations and interactions to earn stars to increase your inventory-size and unlock new areas. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic physics system to play with ⚾</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find many different forms of life 🐌</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50 items to discover 🔎</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 stars to collect 🌟</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Around 1-2 hours of playtime ⏱️</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Music and Sound Design by jaco &quot;bbtombo&quot;!</p>",
